We Deliver 2 Billion Forecasts Per Day

2,000 new subscribers a day | 1,700,000 customers | 20+ weather APIs

   Get current weather, daily forecast for 16 days, and 3-hourly forecast
   5 days for your city. Helpful stats, graphics, and this day in history
   charts are available for your reference. Interactive maps show
   precipitation, clouds, pressure, wind around your location.
   More weather in your city
     __________________________________________________________________

   [hourlybanner.png]

Hourly Weather Forecast for 4 days

   Hourly forecast for 4 days is the accurate and detailed forecast with
   more advanced features in comparison with other forecasts we provide:
     * Higher geographic accuracy - weather model grid with improved
       degrees step
     * More detailed forecast - 96 timestamps
     * Weather data for any location including over 200,000 cities
     * You can request by geo coordinates, city name, ZIP codes

   More information in our Documantation. Contact us
   info@openweathermap.org.
   Try it right now
     __________________________________________________________________

Dashboard for Agricultural Monitoring

   Dashboard is a service where you can visually operate with satellite
   imagery and weather data for your fields. Just draw a polygon in the
   simple interface and immediately get:
     * New Satellite imagery every 2-4 days
     * Historical satellite data archive
     * NDVI / EVI vegetation indices
     * Historical NDVI chart

   More information on the Dashboad page. Contact us
   info@openweathermap.org.
   About Dashboard
   [dashboardbanner.png]
     __________________________________________________________________

   Daily satellite map

Agricultural API for Satellite and Weather data

   This is a set of APIs that can provide Satellite imagery, Weather data
   and other products for agriculture, based on geodata. You can easily
   power your application with a combination of satellite and weather
   data.

     * New Satellite data every 2-4 days (Sentinel-2 and Landsat 8)
     * Historical Satellite and Weather archive data
     * NDVI & EVI indices
     * Soil temperature and moisture

   More information on www.agromonitoring.com. Contact us
   info@openweathermap.org.
   Go to agromonitoring.com
